org.apache.flink.runtime.state.internal

接口 InternalAggregatingState<N,IN,OUT>

  • 类型参数:
    N - The type of the namespace
    IN - Type of the value added to the state.
    OUT - Type of the value extracted from the state.
    所有超级接口:
    AggregatingState<IN,OUT>, AppendingState<IN,OUT>, InternalAppendingState<N,IN,OUT>, InternalKvState<N>, InternalMergingState<N,IN,OUT>, MergingState<IN,OUT>, State
    所有已知实现类:
    HeapAggregatingState, RocksDBAggregatingState

    public interface InternalAggregatingState<N,IN,OUT>
extends InternalMergingState<N,IN,OUT>, AggregatingState<IN,OUT>
    The peer to the AggregatingState in the internal state type hierarchy.

    See InternalKvState for a description of the internal state hierarchy.
